data.description: Welcome home to 545 Providence Circle, a lovely open concept 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home with a full partially finished basement on a private fenced lot in Statham, GA. The cozy living room with vaulted ceiling and fireplace is a great place to unwind. The remodeled kitchen boasts Quartz countertops, ample cabinetry, and access to the back deck allow for entertaining. The garage has been partially enclosed - providing extra space for an office, gym, or flex room. The basement is partially finished and stubbed for an additional bathroom. With LVP flooring, no HOA, and easy access to Athens, Bethlehem, and Winder, this home has it all. Schedule your showing today!
